content:
Hi there! I am Daniel, a software engineer based in Switzerland. Originally from Romania, I obtained my bachelor degree in Computer Engineering at the Polytechnic University in Timișoara. Presently, I am living in the picturesque alpine nation pursuing my interest in life sciences by studying Computational Biology and Bioinformatics at ETH Zürich.
I am passionate about technology and I’m always down to engage in constructive discussions about various topics. I enjoy spending time with motivated people who share my curiosity and drive to learn more about the world.
During my downtime, you can find me hiking, playing tennis or reading a book.
